<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Payment Receipt - Festival App</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
    table, td {
      mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
      mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
    }
    img {
      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      border: 0;
      height: auto;
      line-height: 100%;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .email-header .logo {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .email-body h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .email-body p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .receipt-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9fafb 0%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .receipt-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .receipt-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin: 0 0 5px 0;
    }
    .receipt-value {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .amount-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .amount-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .amount-value {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #10b981;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .receipt-details {
      border-top: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .detail-label {
      display: table-cell;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .detail-value {
      display: table-cell;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #374151;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .success-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #065f46;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .email-footer p {
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #6366f1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper { padding: 20px 10px; }
      .email-header { padding: 25px 20px; }
      .email-header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
      .email-body { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .email-footer { padding: 25px 20px; }
      .button { display: block; padding: 16px 24px; }
      .receipt-card { padding: 20px; }
      .amount-value { font-size: 28px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <div class="email-container">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="email-header">
              <div class="logo">&#128179;</div>
              <h1>Recu de paiement</h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Body -->
            <div class="email-body">
              <h2>Merci pour votre paiement, {{firstName}} !</h2>

              <p>Votre paiement a ete traite avec succes. Voici les details de votre transaction :</p>

              <!-- Receipt Card -->
              <div class="receipt-card">
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <p class="receipt-title">Reference</p>
                      <p class="receipt-value">{{payment.id}}</p>
                    </td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">
                      <span class="success-badge">Paye</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="amount-section">
                  <p class="amount-label">Montant total</p>
                  <p class="amount-value">{{payment.amount}}</p>
                </div>

                <div class="receipt-details">
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date du paiement</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{payment.createdAt}}</span>
                  </div>
                  {{#if payment.paymentMethod}}
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Mode de paiement</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{payment.paymentMethod}}</span>
                  </div>
                  {{/if}}
                  <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Statut</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{payment.status}}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{paymentsUrl}}" class="button">Voir l'historique des paiements</a>
              </div>

              <div class="divider"></div>

              <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>Conservez ce recu</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Ce recu fait office de justificatif de paiement. Vous pouvez le retrouver a tout moment dans votre espace personnel.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="email-footer">
              <p>Besoin d'aide ? Contactez-nous a <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
              <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Festival App. Tous droits reserves.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
